               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <subc>II,1</subc>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሊቃናተ፡ ኢታመጕጽ፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">πρεσβυτέρῳ μὴ ἐπιπλήξῃς</foreign> <ref cRef="1 Tim." loc="5,1">1 Tim. 5,1</ref> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘያመጕጽ፡ ሊቃናተ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Clem." loc="161.">Clem. f. 161.</ref> Notio ex his locis haud satis certe definiri potest ob ambiguitatem vocis <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἐπιπλήσσειν</foreign>, quae <sense n="1" xml:id="D1"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> incutere </quote></cit> 
</sense> <sense n="2" xml:id="D2"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> increpare </quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> objurgare </quote></cit> significat. Collatis arab. verbis <foreign xml:lang="ar">مَقَطَ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> percussit fuste; humi prostravit; iratus fuit </quote></cit> alicui; <foreign xml:lang="ar">وَقَذَ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">وَقَطَ</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="ar">وَقَظَ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> vehementer percussit, prostravit humi </quote></cit>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">وَقَذَ</foreign> IV <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> male affectum reliquit </quote></cit> aliquem, verbo Aethiopico significatio <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> vim inferre, insultare </quote></cit> attribuenda fuerit. Ludolfus ait: „<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> objurgavit et quidem acriter </quote></cit>.“ – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታመጕጽ፡ ዘ፡ ታስተቈጥዕ፡</foreign>; <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> aliud </quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታስተቃልል፡ ወቦእለሂ፡ ታስትት፡</foreign>; <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> aliud </quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታጻላ።</foreign> 
</sense> </sense>
               
